# The Mediaflick Web Project

- is a nextjs 15 Application 
- using pnpm
- using shadcn
- shadcn is already initialized with pnpm dlx shadcn@latest init
- shadcn components installed: button card select input table
- the command to install new components is pnpm dlx shadcn@latest and NOT pnpm dlx shadcn-ui@latest
- using tailwindcss for styling
- using tailwindcss-motion for animations
- Endpoints are located in mediaflick/src/lib/api/endpoints.ts

